vine.util

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • vine.util.Log

  • public final class Log
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides a proxy for logging with a smarter syntax. Use the unchecked methods to place a guard if statement around logs with concatenation. The regular log methods should not be guarded.
    Author:
    Steffen
